          "notice": "Allow users to deposit liquidity (simplified for demo). In production, this would be a proper LP deposit with token management."
        },
        "getCurrentTick()": {
          "notice": "Get the current tick in the pool (price position). In a real implementation, this would come from a Uniswap-style pool. For demo, we return the stored state."
